                        <span class="toggle-icon" id="toggle-2">‚ñº</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stage-details" id="details-2">
                        <span class="ai-skill-label">AI SKILLS</span>
                        <div class="skill-description">
                            <strong>Voice-to-Text Conversation Facilitation:</strong> Use AI voice recorders or speech-to-text tools to have a conversation out loud with an AI. Dump your jumbled thoughts, then copy/paste the transcript into an LLM to help organize and clarify where your head is at.
                            <br><br>
                            <strong>Initial Gap Analysis:</strong> Ask the AI to identify what gaps exist in your initial thinking‚Äîwhat's missing, what needs exploration, what assumptions you're making.
                        </div>
                        <div class="mishap-alert">
                            <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Watch Out:</strong> AI Purgatory - If you're spending more time iterating with AI than it would take to think it through yourself, step back. See the Mishaps tab for guidance.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Stage 3 -->
                <div class="stage-small">
                    <span class="stage-number">3</span>
                    <span class="stage-title">Hypothesis Formation / Question Framing</span>
                </div>

                <!-- Stage 4 - Highlighted with Toggle -->
                <div class="stage-large">
                    <div class="stage-header" onclick="toggleStage(4)">
                        <span class="stage-number">4</span>
                        <span class="stage-title">Research, Angle Discovery & Stakeholder Consideration</span>
                        <span class="toggle-icon" id="toggle-4">‚ñº</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stage-details" id="details-4">
                        <span class="ai-skill-label">AI SKILLS</span>
                        <div class="skill-description">
                            <strong>Gap Analysis (After Angle Selection):</strong> Once you've chosen your angle, ask the AI: "Based on this angle, what gaps exist in my research? What perspectives am I missing? What questions haven't I asked?"
                            <br><br>
                            This helps you identify blind spots in your chosen approach and ensures you're considering the full landscape of stakeholders and perspectives.
                        </div>
                        <div class="mishap-alert">
                            <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Watch Out:</strong> AI Off the Rails - If AI keeps giving you incorrect info, that's a signal you need better primary data. See the Mishaps tab.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Stage 5 -->
                <div class="stage-small">
                    <span class="stage-number">5</span>
                    <span class="stage-title">Source Identification & Outreach</span>
