                <div class="stage-large">
                    <div class="stage-header" onclick="toggleStage(6)">
                        <span class="stage-number">6</span>
                        <span class="stage-title">Interviewing & Primary Reporting</span>
                        <span class="toggle-icon" id="toggle-6">‚ñº</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stage-details" id="details-6">
                        <span class="ai-skill-label">AI SKILLS</span>
                        <div class="skill-description">
                            <strong>Resource Priming:</strong> Record your interviews and convert them to searchable text using transcription tools. This makes it much easier to reference specific quotes and themes later.
                            <br><br>
                            Resource priming is about using LLMs to make your reference materials easier to comprehend and navigate‚Äîturning audio into organized, searchable text is a prime example.
                        </div>
                    </div>
